WEBVTT

00:08:28.677 --> 00:08:30.250
or even yelling at them.

00:08:30.869 --> 00:08:32.827
You have to make that change happen

00:08:33.504 --> 00:08:34.977
through a revolution.

00:08:35.761 --> 00:08:40.269
Now, please don't worry --
I promise you, here, now, today,

00:08:40.293 --> 00:08:42.293
our body count will be very low.

00:08:42.317 --> 00:08:44.546
(Laughter)

00:08:44.570 --> 00:08:48.223
So, now before I get to my four-point
plan for the revolution --

00:08:48.247 --> 00:08:49.888
yes, I have a four-point plan --

00:08:49.912 --> 00:08:52.729
I have two pieces of very good
and important news for you.

00:08:52.753 --> 00:08:53.984
Good news number one:

00:08:54.008 --> 00:08:56.341
there are female filmmakers.

00:08:56.365 --> 00:08:57.618
(Cheers and applause)

00:08:57.642 --> 00:08:59.069
Yes! I know!

00:08:59.093 --> 00:09:00.250
(Applause)